org.spongepowered.api.event.entity

Interface DestructEntityEvent

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Event, MessageChannelEvent, MessageEvent, TargetEntityEvent
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    DestructEntityEvent.Death

    public interface DestructEntityEvent
extends TargetEntityEvent, MessageChannelEvent
    An event where the Entity is being either removed usually due to the Entity being marked as "dead". Happens before HarvestEntityEvent.
